>> I'M NOT CERTAIN NEBRASKA

19:07.246 --> 19:08.914
POLICY MAKERS WERE REALLY

19:08.914 --> 19:10.549
PREPARED FOR WHAT WAS GOING TO

19:10.549 --> 19:11.917
HAPPEN.

