YOU WERE STARTING TO SEE MORE

19:13.185 --> 19:14.720
POSSESSION CASES, YOU WERE

19:14.720 --> 19:16.489
STARTING TO SEE MORE DRIVING

19:16.489 --> 19:18.090
UNDER THE INFLUENCE CASES.

19:18.090 --> 19:19.725
BUT THERE WAS, I THINK, A LITTLE

19:19.725 --> 19:21.360
BIT OF THE DEER-IN-THE-

19:21.360 --> 19:22.695
HEADLIGHTS FEELING THAT WE DON'T

19:22.695 --> 19:24.530
KNOW WHAT THE APPROPRIATE

19:24.530 --> 19:26.699
RESPONSE IS.

19:26.699 --> 19:27.867
>> Reporter: SOME NEBRASKAN

19:27.867 --> 19:29.402
LAWMAKERS BELIEVE THAT THE

19:29.402 --> 19:31.170
APPROPRIATE RESPONSE IS TO

19:31.170 --> 19:32.171
CHANGE THE STATE'S MARIJUANA

19:32.171 --> 19:34.173
LAWS.

19:34.173 --> 19:35.408
BUT THERE ARE MANY DIFFERENT

19:35.408 --> 19:36.942
IDEAS ABOUT WHAT TO DO: ONE

19:36.942 --> 19:38.711
WOULD BE TO LEGALIZE MEDICAL

19:38.711 --> 19:41.714
CANNABIS WHILE ANOTHER WOULD

19:41.714 --> 19:43.315
INCREASE THE FINES FOR EDIBLE

19:43.315 --> 19:45.251
MARIJUANA PRODUCTS.

19:45.251 --> 19:46.519
THE PENALTIES IN NEBRASKA DEPEND

19:46.519 --> 19:48.220
ON HOW MUCH POT IS IN YOUR

19:48.220 --> 19:49.321
POSSESSION.

19:49.321 --> 19:51.123
A FIRST TIME OFFENSE, UNDER AN

19:51.123 --> 19:52.558
OUNCE, IS A $300 FINE.

19:52.558 --> 19:54.627
MORE THAN AN OUNCE BUT LESS THAN

19:54.627 --> 19:56.062
A POUND IS A MISDEMEANOR WITH

19:56.062 --> 19:57.563
POSSIBLE JAIL TIME AND A FINE.

19:57.563 --> 19:59.098
BUT MORE THAN A POUND IS A

19:59.098 --> 20:00.533
FELONY WITH A MAXIMUM FIVE YEARS

20:00.533 --> 20:02.068
IN PRISON AND OR A $10,000 FINE.

20:02.068 --> 20:03.502
WHILE NEBRASKA DELIBERATES

20:03.502 --> 20:05.104
WHETHER TO ALLOW MARIJUANA OR

20:05.104 --> 20:06.672
KEEP IT OUT OF THE STATE, SOME

20:06.672 --> 20:08.174
RESIDENTS LIKE JEREMY CRARY FIND

20:08.174 --> 20:10.142
THEMSELVES CAUGHT BETWEEN THE

20:10.142 --> 20:12.511
LAWS OF NEBRASKA AND COLORADO.

20:12.511 --> 20:14.146
NINE YEARS AGO CRARY ACCIDENTLY

20:14.146 --> 20:15.648
SHOT HIMSELF IN THE HEAD WHILE

20:15.648 --> 20:17.416
PLAYING WITH A GUN.

20:17.416 --> 20:19.218
AFTER PAINFUL SURGERIES AND

20:19.218 --> 20:20.986
PHYSICAL THERAPY, HE SPENT YEARS

20:20.986 --> 20:22.254
ON MORE THAN A DOZEN MEDICATIONS

20:22.254 --> 20:24.490
AND RECEIVED REGULAR SHOTS OF

20:24.490 --> 20:26.592
BOTOX FOR SEVERE MUSCLE SPASMS,

20:26.592 --> 20:28.194
BUT RECENTLY HE STARTED TAKING

20:28.194 --> 20:29.929
MEDICAL CANNABIS INSTEAD.

20:29.929 --> 20:31.330
HE SAYS IT'S THE MOST EFFECTIVE

20:31.330 --> 20:32.565
IN RELIEVING HIS PAIN AND

20:32.565 --> 20:34.667
SPASMS.

