HE SAYS THE STRAINS OF MARIJUANA

20:45.711 --> 20:47.246
HE CAN LEGALLY PURCHASE IN

20:47.246 --> 20:48.747
COLORADO ARE BETTER FOR HIS PAIN

20:48.747 --> 20:49.949
THAN WHAT HE CAN GET ILLEGALLY

20:49.949 --> 20:51.650
IN HIS AREA.

